{"tid":1145163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：中國奢想拖拉至跟拜登談判","createTime":"2019-05-08T13:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T18:05:32.000Z","uid":14918,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8684675e37fb24c55b880cdd881aa0b2069c689f","tid":1145163,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"【中美貿易戰】特朗普：中國奢想拖拉至跟拜登談判<br />\n美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）在Twitter再談中美貿易談判，指出中方之所以在談判上拖拖拉拉，是因為奢想可拖至拜登上台，與之談判，並直斥這種想法不可能實現。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普發帖指：<br />\n<br />\n中國撤回和企圖重新談判貿易協議的原因，是中方真誠地希望，將來能夠與拜登（Joe Biden）這個非常軟弱的民主黨人談判，從而在未來數年繼續摧毀美國。<br />\n<br />\n但他續指，這情況不會發生，他剛剛接獲中方通知，副總理劉鶴正前往美國達成協議。他又稱，很滿意每年徵得超過1000億美元的關稅，以填補美國國庫，形容這對美國是好事，卻對中國不利。"},{"pid":"d56b90cf7fccdc4782fd62636ce3c17393178b7b","tid":1145163,"uid":14918,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2345000/2346073/twt_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2345000%2F2346073%2Ftwt_600.jpg&h=14560933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2345000/2346073/twt2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2345000%2F2346073%2Ftwt2_600.jpg&h=99a0e5c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3988325a8fbc790c55e009b9bb37f53593343f25","tid":1145163,"uid":17641,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>事到如今，中國唯有出兵攻打美國先係上策</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403c022128fb49b30752ad00844e363145ddf6ac","tid":1145163,"uid":196750,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:41:48.000Z","msg":"侵侵借力打力，順便陰民主黨一把，真係政治天才。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n低層出身易貪錢。藍領拜登繼續企出嚟替中共辯護囉，不過唔知會唔會畀個黨按住呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f13ccfbad6e18305273b28155e60f0a354ef34","tid":1145163,"uid":90521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"403c022128fb49b30752ad00844e363145ddf6ac","tid":1145163,"uid":196750,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:41:48.000Z","msg":"侵侵借力打力，順便陰民主黨一把，真係政治天才。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n低層出身易貪錢。藍領拜登繼續企出嚟替中共辯護囉，不過唔知會唔會畀個黨按住呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"拜登話唔打中國既民主黨班人反佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95cdf9e32ba47e31b6c36afbc34dadbe13ad969","tid":1145163,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631ab7f67889d88b673ceeb430e22678816fd51b","tid":1145163,"uid":48334,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"特朗普口出狂言，支持習帝親率大軍征美<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73e980473cc0ce67435505367b0a441a4c3ddb9","tid":1145163,"uid":124116,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://joebiden.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjoebiden.info%2F&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=70ff4f07\" target=\"_blank\">https://joebiden.info/</a>"},{"pid":"b000d99f2a99ea544925dc5aaae1ceba69134eca","tid":1145163,"uid":53498,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3988325a8fbc790c55e009b9bb37f53593343f25","tid":1145163,"uid":17641,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>事到如今，中國唯有出兵攻打美國先係上策</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"r